            . I am a shopman to Mr. Cording, No. 38, Aldgate High-street, pawnbroker. On the 6th of November, the prisoner came to the shop and pawned a pair of trousers and a waistcoat, which I produce, for 6s - I did not know him before - I am certain of him.</p>
